{
  "stem": "268.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And sometimes cut out pieces of-- and sewing a piece of a yellow star of David, so that you couldn't escape or have torn clothes, painted on your back.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But at least the clothes were much better than concentration camp clothes, which were a lot later.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Because this was at least regular cotton or wool.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "It was warmer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "So this guy addresses us from his podium.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Again, a really tall figure, boots, and brown shirt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And swastika and his cap, typical square cap.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And shouts, you know, the usual [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Nothing will happen to you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "You're here to be productive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And if you obey orders, and do your work right, you will live, you will exist.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And for those of you who ever entertained the idea of escaping, we have some other surprises for you.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he gave a sort of an orientation speech.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing in welcoming tones, mind you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as he finishes, then the guy takes over after him who was a Jewish prisoner who was called the lageralteste.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Actually, the lageralteste-- to explain the prison hierarchy a little bit-- it was-- a lageralteste was really the commandant, because he had the say so in the whole camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He accounted to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Germans wouldn't be bothered with details.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He just wanted to make sure that everything functions properly, and the work is being done.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No one escapes, and don't bother me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the lageralteste, he was-- in English terms, would be a trustee.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was, of course, in charge of the whole camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He had under him [GERMAN], which was one who was in charge of the block, which is a barrack.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then each barrack would be divided into six stuben, meaning rooms.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
